thread.title: LARRY LEFFLER and Mary Leffler
thread.title_full: Superior Van and Mobility reviewed by LARRY LEFFLER and Mary Leffler

author: LARRY LEFFLER and Mary Leffler
title: LARRY LEFFLER and Mary Leffler
text: Excellent service. Ed brought a van to size up what I needed to my home. I picked a van out of the inventory on the internet and Ed got it and brought it to my home and I bought it. Didn't even have to leave my home.
